538
00:33:11,710 --> 00:33:13,850
Her mom is recovering quickly.

539
00:33:13,850 --> 00:33:15,520
I'm sure she'll find her footing again soon,

540
00:33:15,520 --> 00:33:17,370
then, our relationship can get back on track.

541
00:33:17,370 --> 00:33:18,610
Wait, didn't you give up?

542
00:33:18,610 --> 00:33:20,810
Give up*? Are you counting cabbages?
(Sounds like 'cabbage')

543
00:33:20,810 --> 00:33:23,140
Wow, how are you joking in this situation?

544
00:33:23,140 --> 00:33:24,870
What?

545
