547
00:33:28,380 --> 00:33:30,640
Hyeon Ju and I are just

548
00:33:30,640 --> 00:33:32,510
on break right now.

549
00:33:34,360 --> 00:33:36,510
I'll wait.

550
00:33:36,510 --> 00:33:38,880
Until she opens her heart again.

551
00:33:40,830 --> 00:33:43,170
Optimism is a disease.

552
00:33:43,170 --> 00:33:46,080
You're terminal, you brother-in-law.

553
00:33:46,080 --> 00:33:49,060
Took you long enough to notice, bro-in-law.

554
00:33:49,060 --> 00:33:52,120
Man, I'm seriously jealous of Ui Jun.

