with you and feel the winter wind.

573
00:34:38,210 --> 00:34:41,110
<i>You must've felt trapped and suffocated.</i>

574
00:34:41,110 --> 00:34:42,820
Thank you.

575
00:34:43,660 --> 00:34:46,610
I'm sorry I made you worry with what I said.

576
00:34:48,310 --> 00:34:51,420
