582
00:35:02,640 --> 00:35:03,810
What?

583
00:35:03,810 --> 00:35:05,650
I feel like I've been reborn.

584
00:35:05,650 --> 00:35:08,790
After going through something that dark,

585
00:35:11,380 --> 00:35:13,280
