586
00:35:13,280 --> 00:35:17,200
I want to live each moment to the fullest extent.

587
00:35:17,200 --> 00:35:19,140
With you.

588
00:35:21,770 --> 00:35:23,840
<i>Don't be bound to the past.</i>

589
00:35:23,840 --> 00:35:26,610
<i>from now on, I hope you become happy.</i>

590
00:35:27,610 --> 00:35:29,890
<i>For the sake of Geum Ju, who is by your side.</i>

591
00:35:29,890 --> 00:35:31,780
I love it.

592
00:35:50,860 --> 00:35:52,820
Yes, Ui Jun. Where did you go?

593
00:35:52,820 --> 00:35:54,420
<i>Outside the window.</i>

594
00:35:54,420 --> 00:35:56,220
<i>Look down.</i>

595
00:35:57,470 --> 00:36:00,260
[I Heart U]

596
00:36:00,260 --> 00:36:05,190
<i>♫ If I were to list the reasons I like you ♫</i>

597
00:36:06,590 --> 00:36:08,840
What the?

598
00:36:12,200 --> 00:36:15,110
I love you, too!

599
00:36:16,260 --> 00:36:21,460
<i>♫ You are stuck to my heart ♫</i>

600
00:36:21,460 --> 00:36:27,800
<i>♫ You smell like the gentle scent of soap ♫</i>

601
00:36:27,800 --> 00:36:30,020
Smile.

602
00:36:32,900 --> 00:36:40,320
<i>♫ All the seasons I spent with you ♫</i>

603
00:36:41,610 --> 00:36:44,140
So fluffy.

604
00:36:44,140 --> 00:36:49,700
<i>♫ If I were to list the reasons I like you ♫</i>

605
00:36:49,700 --> 00:36:55,250
<i>♫ I would need all night to count them ♫</i>

606
00:36:55,250 --> 00:37:00,790
<i>♫ The warmth in your eyes
when you look at me ♫</i>

607
00:37:00,790 --> 00:37:05,680
<i>♫ The biggest reason is just you ♫</i>

608
00:37:05,680 --> 00:37:09,420
<i>♫ 'Cause it's you ♫</i>

609
00:37:12,010 --> 00:37:15,240
Hey. I can do it by myself.

610
00:37:15,240 --> 00:37:17,470
I told you to leave. Why are you still here?

611
00:37:17,470 --> 00:37:19,010
Hand it over.

612
00:37:19,010 --> 00:37:22,000
You said you wanted to clean
everything before she's discharged.

613
00:37:22,000 --> 00:37:24,110
You must be tired from going
to the hospital this morning.

614
00:37:24,110 --> 00:37:26,100
You'll get sick if you do it by yourself.

615
00:37:26,100 --> 00:37:30,200
Girl, you brought so much food to my mom, too.

616
00:37:30,220 --> 00:37:32,710
She was so thankful.

617
00:37:32,710 --> 00:37:36,110
No need to thank me. Of course, I should do that.

618
00:37:36,110 --> 00:37:39,050
She cared for us so deeply

619
00:37:39,050 --> 00:37:42,500
when my brother and I had nowhere to lean on.

620
00:37:42,500 --> 00:37:47,790
Your mom is practically my real mom.

621
00:37:47,790 --> 00:37:51,250
So, you and I are basically family.

622
00:37:56,650 --> 00:38:00,600
That's why I can't forget what she said.

623
00:38:00,600 --> 00:38:04,170
I hope my Hyeon Ju meets
someone nice like you did.

624
00:38:04,170 --> 00:38:05,650
Because I'm stuck here like this,

625
00:38:05,650 --> 00:38:09,450
