631
00:38:22,450 --> 00:38:24,960
Someone sweet and hard-working.

632
00:38:25,860 --> 00:38:29,330
My mom is still worried about me while sick...

633
00:38:30,320 --> 00:38:31,700
Hand me the rag.

634
00:38:31,700 --> 00:38:35,700
So, you should date, so she doesn't worry.

635
00:38:35,700 --> 00:38:38,830
I have someone in mind.

636
00:38:38,830 --> 00:38:39,620
What?

637
00:38:39,620 --> 00:38:41,010
You know the son of the Bochun Gas Station owner?

638
00:38:41,010 --> 00:38:43,050
He got divorced last year and is living alone.

639
00:38:43,050 --> 00:38:44,570
Look.

640
00:38:45,850 --> 00:38:48,150
He's good-looking and tall.

641
00:38:48,150 --> 00:38:50,620
Leave it. It's not the right time.

642
00:38:50,620 --> 00:38:53,000
This is the perfect time!

643
00:38:53,000 --> 00:38:55,510
This is a chance for you to be a good daughter.

644
00:38:55,510 --> 00:38:58,020
Help your mom worry less.

645
00:38:58,020 --> 00:38:59,720
A much better way is to

646
00:38:59,720 --> 00:39:01,970
boost the pension revenue.

647
00:39:01,970 --> 00:39:04,170
Great, he has a killer network.

648
00:39:04,170 --> 00:39:05,380
He knows everyone.

649
00:39:05,380 --> 00:39:07,150
He'll boost pension revenue for sure.

650
00:39:07,150 --> 00:39:09,880
Meet him, even if it's just for business.

651
00:39:10,660 --> 00:39:12,190
- Hey...
- Hello?

652
00:39:12,190 --> 00:39:14,430
Hello, I'm Ms. Bong from the car center.

653
00:39:14,430 --> 00:39:16,470
How are you doing?

654
00:39:17,800 --> 00:39:21,800
Yes, I was just wondering.
What are you doing today?

655
00:39:23,620 --> 00:39:26,040
What? What's Hyeon Ju doing?

656
00:39:26,040 --> 00:39:28,360
Can't you tell? She's on a blind date.

657
00:39:28,360 --> 00:39:30,940
With the Bochun Gas Station owner's son.

658
00:39:30,940 --> 00:39:33,740
Looked like Seon Hwa put it together.

659
00:39:33,740 --> 00:39:35,670
Seon Hwa did?

660
00:39:37,500 --> 00:39:42,200
He looks way older than Hyeon Ju.

661
00:39:43,390 --> 00:39:45,410
I'm leaving.

662
00:39:45,410 --> 00:39:48,640
Hey, hey. Bong Seon Uk! Where are you going?

663
00:39:58,300 --> 00:39:59,520
Oh, right.

664
00:39:59,520 --> 00:40:01,830
I meant to drop by the supermarket.

665
00:40:01,830 --> 00:40:03,700
Oh, yeah?

666
00:40:03,700 --> 00:40:05,730
Head in first. I'll go.

667
00:40:05,730 --> 00:40:07,690
Will you?

668
00:40:07,700 --> 00:40:10,500
- Text me what you need.
- Okay.

669
00:40:22,070 --> 00:40:23,770
Geum Ju.

670
00:40:38,550 --> 00:40:41,530
<i>Happy birthday, Ui Jun!</i>

671
00:40:44,290 --> 00:40:47,260
<i>Thank you for being by my side during tough times.</i>

672
00:40:47,260 --> 00:40:50,140
<i>With you by my side, I was able to endure</i>

673
00:40:50,140 --> 00:40:51,920
<i>and persevere.</i>

674
00:40:51,920 --> 00:40:55,030
<i>I promise to pay back your kindness.</i>

675
00:40:55,030 --> 00:40:57,490
<i>I'll always be your strength, too.</i>

676
00:40:57,490 --> 00:40:59,820
<i>I'll always be by your side.</i>

677
00:40:59,820 --> 00:41:01,640
<i>Thank you, Ui Jun.</i>

678
00:41:01,640 --> 00:41:03,890
<i>I love you.</i>

679
00:41:08,540 --> 00:41:13,320
<i>♫ Happy birthday to you ♫</i>

680
00:41:13,320 --> 00:41:17,780
<i>♫ Happy birthday to you ♫</i>

681
00:41:17,780 --> 00:41:22,660
<i>♫ Happy birthday to you, dear Ui Jun ♫</i>

682
00:41:22,660 --> 00:41:28,070
<i>♫ Happy birthday to you ♫</i>

683
00:41:29,680 --> 00:41:32,400
Oh, wait, wait. Make a wish.

684
00:41:33,420 --> 00:41:34,860
Okay.

685
00:41:51,030 --> 00:41:53,080
What did you wish for?

686
00:41:59,750 --> 00:42:01,510
That this happiness

687
00:42:03,610 --> 00:42:07,330
never shatters.

688
00:42:17,090 --> 00:42:22,360
<i>♫ If rivers take you out afar ♫</i>

689
00:42:23,880 --> 00:42:28,980
<i>♫ If you're almost at the shore ♫</i>

690
00:42:32,260 --> 00:42:34,260
Happy birthday.

691
00:42:35,060 --> 00:42:36,660
Thank you.

692
00:42:38,300 --> 00:42:43,630
<i>♫ Hold on tight through it all ♫</i>

693
00:42:45,230 --> 00:42:50,410
<i>♫ Hold on tight through it all ♫</i>

694
00:42:51,390 --> 00:42:58,190
<i>♫ Stay with me, I'll always be, too ♫</i>

695
00:42:58,190 --> 00:43:03,500
<i>♫ Even if you're not there,
I'll be there for you ♫</i>

696
00:43:03,500 --> 00:43:07,200
<i>♫ In the whole world ♫</i>

697
00:43:09,380 --> 00:43:13,540
<i>♫ Hold on tight through it all ♫</i>

698
00:44:44,960 --> 00:44:48,090
[Lake Bochun Pension]

699
00:44:59,380 --> 00:45:01,340
Seon Uk?

700
00:45:06,690 --> 00:45:08,510
Noona.

701
00:45:08,510 --> 00:45:10,710
What are you doing here?

702
00:45:12,090 --> 00:45:14,340
Are you drunk?

703
00:45:14,340 --> 00:45:17,100
How long have you been out here like this?

704
00:45:17,100 --> 00:45:19,490
Are you trying to freeze to death?

705
00:45:19,490 --> 00:45:21,200
I'm sorry...

706
00:45:23,830 --> 00:45:25,360
But I have something I need to say.

707
00:45:25,360 --> 00:45:27,580
Go home. I've got nothing to say to you.

708
00:45:27,580 --> 00:45:29,870
Are you going to keep seeing that guy?

709
00:45:31,680 --> 00:45:33,910
Bochun Gas Station owner's son?

710
00:45:36,190 --> 00:45:38,750
Do you plan on continuing to see him?

711
00:45:44,350 --> 00:45:46,720
That's none of your business.

712
00:45:47,840 --> 00:45:49,460
You're right.

713
00:45:53,200 --> 00:45:54,580
I-

714
00:45:55,990 --> 00:45:58,320
I know it's none of my business...

715
00:46:00,610 --> 00:46:02,690
but can you please not see him?

716
00:46:05,700 --> 00:46:07,140
What?

717
00:46:15,000 --> 00:46:17,140
Please don't see him.

718
00:46:19,740 --> 00:46:21,120
Please?

719
00:46:26,070 --> 00:46:28,080
Hey, what's with you?

720
00:46:28,080 --> 00:46:30,420
Seon Uk. Bong Seon Uk...

721
00:46:30,420 --> 00:46:32,910
Seon Uk. Bong Seon Uk.

722
00:46:32,910 --> 00:46:35,260
Come to your senses.

723
00:46:55,000 --> 00:46:56,960
Hyeon Ju...

724
00:47:02,600 --> 00:47:04,430
Get your hands off him.

725
00:47:07,420 --> 00:47:08,930
I said move your hand.

726
00:47:08,930 --> 00:47:11,010
S-Seon Hwa.

727
00:47:16,330 --> 00:47:19,280
Young Woong, I found Seon Uk. Come get him.

728
00:47:20,180 --> 00:47:22,350
He's at Hyeon Ju's pension.

729
00:47:39,820 --> 00:47:43,490
You flat-out rejected the gas
station guy's second date.

730
00:47:43,490 --> 00:47:45,280
Why did you do that?

731
00:47:47,280 --> 00:47:50,520
Is that what you came to ask me?

732
00:47:50,550 --> 00:47:52,850
Well...

733
00:47:52,850 --> 00:47:56,200
it just didn't feel right...

734
00:47:56,200 --> 00:47:58,840
meeting him with ulterior motives.

735
00:47:58,840 --> 00:48:00,940
Not because of Seon Uk?

736
00:48:01,770 --> 00:48:03,170
What?

737
00:48:08,300 --> 00:48:12,400
By chance, did you know?

738
00:48:13,270 --> 00:48:16,160
<i>Hey. I might just spill everything.</i>

739
00:48:16,160 --> 00:48:18,700
<i>That you like Hyeon Ju.</i>

740
00:48:18,700 --> 00:48:19,700
<i>You love her so much</i>

741
00:48:19,700 --> 00:48:21,800
<i>that you're willing to give away your liver!</i>

742
00:48:21,830 --> 00:48:25,120
<i>Gosh, come on. Be quiet.</i>

743
00:48:25,120 --> 00:48:27,930
<i>Don't cause a scene.</i>

744
00:48:31,120 --> 00:48:34,010
<i>You lunatic.</i>

745
00:48:42,410 --> 00:48:44,820
Why didn't you tell me?

746
00:48:44,820 --> 00:48:47,630
Why did you feign innocence?
You should've told me.

747
00:48:47,630 --> 00:48:49,380
That Seon Uk likes you.

748
00:48:49,380 --> 00:48:52,210
You should've told me you like him, too.

749
00:48:52,210 --> 00:48:54,470
Hey, you think I'm a joke?

750
00:48:54,500 --> 00:48:57,700
Or are you blinded by love that
you don't care about your friend?

751
00:48:57,700 --> 00:49:00,330
No, it's not that...

752
00:49:00,330 --> 00:49:03,700
Even though I felt sick with betrayal,

753
00:49:03,700 --> 00:49:06,390
I still wanted to play ignorant.

754
00:49:06,390 --> 00:49:07,490
What?

755
00:49:07,490 --> 00:49:10,550
I wanted to keep pretending,

756
00:49:11,820 --> 00:49:16,020
so I wouldn't lose you, who's family to me.

757
00:49:17,510 --> 00:49:19,900
- Seon Hwa...
- Hyeon Ju.

758
00:49:20,760 --> 00:49:23,220
I said it clearly.

759
00:49:23,220 --> 00:49:26,390
I asked you nicely, Hyeon Ju.

760
00:49:26,390 --> 00:49:29,060
Gosh, you stupid bitch.

761
00:49:30,300 --> 00:49:32,100
I'm sorry.

762
00:49:32,100 --> 00:49:36,420
But the reason I turned that guy down
wasn't because of Seon Uk.

763
00:49:36,420 --> 00:49:38,660
Shut up. Don't even say Seon Uk's name.

764
00:49:38,660 --> 00:49:40,780
Stay away from us siblings.

765
00:49:40,780 --> 00:49:43,180
Unless you want to see me drown in this lake.

766
00:49:43,180 --> 00:49:44,610
Got it?

767
00:49:44,610 --> 00:49:45,910
S-Seon Hwa!

768
00:49:45,910 --> 00:49:47,590
What?

769
00:49:47,590 --> 00:49:49,720
You still think I'm a joke?

770
00:49:49,720 --> 00:49:52,040
You think I can't do it?

771
00:49:53,300 --> 00:49:55,540
Hey! Bong Seon Hwa!

772
00:49:55,540 --> 00:49:57,950
Hey! Bong Seon Hwa!

773
00:49:57,950 --> 00:49:59,680
Hey!

774
00:49:59,680 --> 00:50:01,330
Let go!

775
00:50:01,330 --> 00:50:03,330
I said let go!

776
00:50:03,330 --> 00:50:05,190
Okay, okay.

777
00:50:05,190 --> 00:50:07,480
I'll do as you say.

778
00:50:07,480 --> 00:50:10,190
Please don't do this. Please?

779
00:50:34,540 --> 00:50:35,800
<i>She even called the hospital</i>

780
00:50:35,800 --> 00:50:38,840
<i>to make sure it suits the diet
for someone post-liver transplant.</i>

781
00:50:38,840 --> 00:50:41,570
<i>Gosh, I'm so grateful.</i>

782
00:50:42,470 --> 00:50:46,910
<i>Your mom is practically my real mom.</i>

783
00:50:47,720 --> 00:50:51,230
<i>So, you and I are basically family.</i>

784
00:51:11,650 --> 00:51:13,160
Ui Jun.

785
00:51:13,160 --> 00:51:14,770
Seo Ui Jun.

786
00:51:15,570 --> 00:51:17,480
Are you in the bathroom?

787
00:51:17,480 --> 00:51:20,050
You should've woken me up.

788
00:51:29,860 --> 00:51:32,130
<i>Something urgent came up, so I had to leave first.</i>

789
00:51:32,130 --> 00:51:33,580
<i>Sorry.</i>

790
00:51:33,580 --> 00:51:35,970
<i>I didn't wake you up because
you were sleeping so soundly.</i>

791
00:51:35,970 --> 00:51:37,580
<i>Don't be upset.</i>

792
00:51:37,580 --> 00:51:40,140
What urgent issue?

793
00:51:47,200 --> 00:51:49,530
<i>The customer is not answering
the phone. After the beep…</i>

794
00:51:49,530 --> 00:51:52,570
What? And he's not picking up?

795
00:51:54,200 --> 00:51:55,560
[Don't be upset]

796
00:51:55,560 --> 00:51:58,600
I'm not upset...

797
00:51:59,540 --> 00:52:02,030
